		<!-- Dashboard Page Start -->

		<div class="page" id="page-dashboard">
			<header class="bp-header cf">
				<h1 class="bp-header__title">Really! Home</h1>
				<p class="bp-header__desc">
					Click This Link, Here you sent messages Privately all the users who created their Account in our Website. Also you can send Global messages and all the Private & Global messages will save on our databse.<br />
					<a href="/chat" target="_blank" title="Go for Messaging">
						Go for Messaging</a><br /><br />
					Click This Link, Here you create Private or Public notes for you. But Public for everyone, anyone can see it's content.<br />
					<a href="/notes" target="_blank" title="Go for Notes">
						Go for Notes</a><br /><br />
					Click This Link, Here you can Join other's room or create an unique room and invite other's and Here messages will not be saved. It's peer to peer messaging system. Those messages will disapear when you refresh the page.<br /><br />
